  <bioghist id="aspace_e7789100cf8d6d3919a6ff4ccebcea32">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>After graduating from Cornell University (M.P.S.) in 1976, Spak-Hoy taught a Medical Care course at Ithaca College.</p>  </bioghist>
